name: r-gparotation
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2022.4-1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-gparotation
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/GPArotation_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/GPArotation/GPArotation_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 231e7edcdcc091fbecfb4f2e88d1a4344967cf7ea58074b385a4b8b48d9da224

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('GPArotation')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('GPArotation')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://www.stat.ucla.edu/research/gpa
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Gradient Projection Algorithm Rotation for Factor Analysis. See ?GPArotation.Intro for more details.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
